Actually, we need a 1 to 9, zeros don\'t work...So using 2 six sided dice we can use
this formula
Die 1:
1-2: Add 0
3-4: Add 3
5-6: Add 6

Die 2:
1-2: 1
3-4: 2
5-6: 3

Pop Mod = 3 x (ceiling(Die1 / 2) - 1) + ceiling(Die2 / 2)

